One of America's leading
young artists, Miss Sader

with a sensilive flair
for intricate design.
For the Orient

a unique tableau of
these familiar attractions-
Typical Chinese Gateway
Daibutsu—giant image of Buddha
Fujiyama
The Torii-formal Japanese Gateway

A Chinese Pagoda, Pedicab
